sentences: Maggie Chiang Mei-chi (Chinese: 江美琪; pinyin:
Jiāng měiqí) is a Taiwanese singer and songwriter.
She is dubbed a "therapeutic singer" (療傷系歌手) by the Chinese-language media for her heartfelt delivery of ballads.
I Love Faye Wong (我愛王菲)
Love at Second Sight (第二眼美女)
Friend of a Friend (朋友的朋友)
Lover's Poem (戀人心中有一首詩)
As Long,As Life (我們都是有歌的人)
Beautiful But Lonely (又寂寞又美麗)
The Weight of Love (愛情的重量)
